Pernambuco Championship 1941

Source: "Campeonato Pernambucano - 1915 a 1970", book written by 
Carlos Celso Cordeiro and Luciano Guedes Cordeiro.
Primeiro Turno
25/05/41 América-PE 1-1 Flamengo (RE)
01/06/41 Sport Recife 7-0 Great Western
08/06/41 Santa Cruz 3-0 Tramways-PE
15/06/41 Náutico 2-2 América-PE
19/06/41 Flamengo (RE) 2-2 Great Western
22/06/41 Sport Recife 5-2 Santa Cruz
26/06/41 Náutico 6-1 Tramways-PE
29/06/41 América-PE 6-3 Great Western
03/07/41 Sport Recife 1-0 Flamengo (RE)
06/07/41 Náutico 5-2 Santa Cruz
10/07/41 Great Western 6-3 Tramways-PE
13/07/41 Sport Recife 3-1 América-PE
16/07/41 Santa Cruz 9-3 Flamengo (RE)
20/07/41 Náutico 2-0 Great Western
24/07/41 América-PE 2-2 Tramways-PE
27/07/41 Náutico 7-1 Flamengo (RE)
31/07/41 Great Western 5-2 Santa Cruz
03/08/41 Sport Recife 6-1 Tramways-PE
07/08/41 América-PE - Santa Cruz   [América won by W.O]
10/08/41 Sport Recife 3-0 Náutico
19/08/41 Tramways-PE 10-1 Flamengo (RE)
