Segundo Turno
24/08/41        Tramways-PE 4-1 Flamengo (RE)
28/08/41        América-PE 2-1 Náutico
31/08/41        Sport Recife 6-1 Tramways-PE
                [Tramways abandoned the championship; their remaining 
                 matches were awarded as lost by W.O.]
07/09/41         América-PE 6-0 Flamengo (RE)
11/09/41         Great Western 2-1 Náutico
14/09/41         Santa Cruz 2-2 Sport Recife
